          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-timothy-beaumont" title="Mr Timothy Beaumont">Lord Beaumont of Whitley</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I shall certainly take the matter away and look at it, but for once, I both understand the answers and accept them. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
