            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_97gc' title='Col. 97GC &mdash; HL Deb 26 November 1996 vol 576 c97GC' name='column_97gc' href='#column_97gc' rel='bookmark'>97GC</a>
            anything happening currently with regard to the International Maritime Organisation? Do the Government propose to take any further initiative? It would be useful for the purpose of the Committee if the Minister could answer those two points.
          </p>
